text: Meowingtons Hax Tour Trax is a studio album. It is by artists who are signed to Deadmau5's record label, Mau5trap. It was made to promote the artists and his Meowingtons Hax Tour, which was named after his cat, Professor Meowingtons. Despite the name, only one of the tracks on the album is by Deadmau5, and the rest are by other artists, including Skrillex, Moguai, Datsik and Feed Me. ==Track listing== Category:2011 albums Category:Deadmau5 albums Category:Virgin Records albums
title: Meowingtons Hax Tour Trax
